Section.description:
The Engineering Programs offered at QIS College of Engineering and Technology are designed for career initiation and growth in the competitive market place. There is equal emphasis on theoretical concepts as well as practical insights, making our programs the right weapons to conquer the career goals. Mission of the college is to impart quality education by continuous development of infrastructure and to provide the state-of-the-art equipment/software.
